search.val: It seems you have provided a link to the Bootstrap CSS framework that is hosted on a content delivery network (CDN). CDNs are used for faster and more reliable access to web resources like stylesheets, scripts, and images by replicating and distributing them across multiple servers worldwide. In this case, the link you provided is pointing to an external stylesheet file for Bootstrap version currently hosted on the CDN. This allows developers to easily incorporate Bootstrap into their projects without having to host the files themselves.
